flowRoot.flowPara: Two Shades of Blue proudly presents a rollicking tale of mystery and adventure, confused nationalities, kick­ass princesses and buried treasure.

Licking his wounds after another botched mission, Indiana Jones returns to Morocco for a stiff drink and a quick cuddle with the girl he walked out on over a year ago. But no sooner are the lovers reunited than disaster strikes – again!
Can Indy find the treasure and the girl and save the day before it’s too late?

Accompanied by his man­-eating mother, devoted man­servant and horse, Indy faces the usual cast of sinisterly­-inept, country­-confused double agents, spies and greedy arch­villains, who would do anything to stop him! Join us for an hour of pun­filled fun, comic exploits, outrageous accents and music you’ll be singing along to for days after, as Indiana Jones and the Pantomime Horse defy villainy to seek the long­ lost Treasure of the Gorgons!
